>\n咁都係鬼?<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫大家忘記咁耐泛民以黎出賣港人既事蹟 反而係應該時時提醒自己留意住泛民隨時蠢蠢欲動<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要令泛民知道 想要你個票 就要配合我地行動 唔好諗住衝出黎搶光環起大台 我地唔怕老解入城 亦都唔會介意全投建制攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e68fe9e15639b0b7ab66a8575eceed682c31121c","tid":1433213,"uid":67249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:43:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">做文宣，儲民意，勿失焦<br />\n<br />\n屌人前，請FC<br />\n<br />\n提防分化撚上綱上線</span>"},{"pid":"7a900192fcd5ae1099f41b483ee4e94b5633ab77","tid":1433213,"uid":92348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:44:34.000Z","msg":"香港人團結左個零兩個月 一有多幾個五毛分化post就即刻無哂腦袋<br />\n不割蓆不分化<br />\n對準政權<br />\n要人講幾多次呀！！！！！"},{"pid":"02d74e3227872a578a564f9a80ff8df91955d705","tid":1433213,"uid":189015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:44:56.000Z","msg":"不分化、不割席、不割灰<br />\nBE HUMBLE"},{"pid":"4eb51aba5a55c6d4e3a0034e6393696864f9ecbf","tid":1433213,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:48:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13fa1b25bcbed6bde28cbcc9449ff210461dd0b3","tid":1433213,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:49:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d2a8c05f7db8ab4d24fbe291560e73386ede995","tid":1433213,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:50:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00a3f424225db2a70f04ca363ca7906acf42dfb2","tid":1433213,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:51:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e45f25321acaff4ed902b5b6fcc5a06ab1a9908","tid":1433213,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:52:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dea4194067a2e5050a2a824caba08b872690c053","tid":1433213,"uid":119899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:53:43.000Z","msg":"真心"},{"pid":"fbef6